{"tid":761303,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"期望越大 失望越大","createTime":"2018-07-30T09:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T13:52:12.000Z","uid":195396,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3705938d190be898ed3ade63ee7230ce0aa82020","tid":761303,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:20:29.000Z","msg":"如果睇緊呢個post嘅你仲年輕 我贈你一句說話<br />\n<br />\n咪撚信 期望越大失望越大 呢一句嘢<br />\n<br />\n呢一句說話講嘅係事實<br />\n期望同失望係成正比<br />\n但係唔代表你唔可以去爭取<br />\n<br />\n怕失望 結果乜都求鳩奇 乜都唔去爭<br />\n最後發現自己乜都無做過<br />\n<br />\n點解唔趁自己仲有本錢去爭啲自己想要嘅嘢<br />\n好過自己乜都唔做 去到最後先發現自己無嘢可以再輸<br />\n<br />\n失望原來真係唔可怕<br />\n我最後悔係自己無期望過 無爭取過<br />\n到頭來時機過咗 本錢無咗 自己乜都無<br />\n只可以怪自己<br />\n<br />\n如果你係一個死攬住呢句嘢嘅人<br />\n希望你唔好好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259a6594f4ef37f91540821e45b43ecade78a790","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6abeaf9a080405d45121ad465c3e4218675fb7b8","tid":761303,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259a6594f4ef37f91540821e45b43ecade78a790","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"好過無爭取過<br />\n諗返以前自己乜都打定輸數 人係豁達啲 但好多嘢根本唔叫得失去 因為連擁有都未試過"},{"pid":"130eadab49a0c92d0b1e190e6caccc5ec2d28d52","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bf09bac90cbf3eae56d9fa23951181f7279bafb","tid":761303,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"130eadab49a0c92d0b1e190e6caccc5ec2d28d52","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6abeaf9a080405d45121ad465c3e4218675fb7b8","tid":761303,"uid":195396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259a6594f4ef37f91540821e45b43ecade78a790","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:38:34.000Z","msg":"好過無爭取過<br />\n諗返以前自己乜都打定輸數 人係豁達啲 但好多嘢根本唔叫得失去 因為連擁有都未試過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"唔係話要擁有好多嘢<br />\n但諗返自己以前好多嘢都係自己判自己死刑<br />\n自己定自己做輸家 真係好on9"},{"pid":"96ccb6291df1b1bf8f2dc8fcd95cff5baca75fde","tid":761303,"uid":68255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"到最尾怕咩無結果 起碼我做過<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n0A775Eyfkw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn0A775Eyfkw&d=FN1IPIf6A5MM2oCOz3XkkzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=61401b24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n0A775Eyfkw</a>"},{"pid":"620e56dc10846ee0c634c6e47a64e2e4c841ed5b","tid":761303,"uid":195431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259a6594f4ef37f91540821e45b43ecade78a790","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:50:31.000Z","msg":"但同時間又會欣慰自己有嘗試到"},{"pid":"58625b683e7bfe151d11e77d293f4a0b64f1e218","tid":761303,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259a6594f4ef37f91540821e45b43ecade78a790","tid":761303,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T09:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"如害怕煩惱 為何期望太高 喎"}]}